<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_290_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> Vns hat <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l13">auf dıſʒ ʒeıt <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef geſandt / den handel <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l14"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd eẅr antreffend / <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l15"><expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ ſıch eẅr <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l16">deſt bas darnach wıſſe <expan>ʒurıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_line_1594199207746_210"><expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
