</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_290" id="144r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Sweinfurt</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf disz zeit
                                <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief gesandt, den handel
                                <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> und ewr antreffend,
                            <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz sich ewr
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> dest bas darnach wisse <expan>zu
                                richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
